  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this is-- was the basic method of Germany, of, of, of the Nazis, if you like to call, whereby they did not alert the world, except of maybe some very keen journalists of which stories are who worked in Berlin in, in the '30s, or in any of these German-occupied countries, who were saying what was going truthfully on.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you know, the bottom line is-- and I've been through Auschwitz-- which is Birkenau, Auschwitz, too, where most of the killing was done-- in Buchenwald, in Reinsdorf, [NON-ENGLISH], and then back to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I've seen probably more dead people than I care to remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "However, the organization of it was absolutely unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "How they were able to hide the facts, how outwardly it was done in a more or less gentlemanly measure, at least in, in Hungary between the 19th of March 1944, and the 4th of July, when our transport was one before the last.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was only one more transport from [NON-ENGLISH], which was the internment camp, which came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Literally, within three months, or three-- exactly three-and-a-half months' time to move and organize over 650,000 people in the midst of the war which they were losing-- you cannot do that unless the local gendarme, who were terrible, police, political parties, and population actively supports it.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If there would have been the least amount of, of, of sympathy, if you like, that we want-- we don't like that to happen to our fellow citizens, they would not have had the time to do it anymore.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that is where I mentioned the, the, the responsibility of the Judenrat of Budapest, which was, in turn, carried out by the local Judenrat, where they denied the knowledge of the death camps.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They, they assured everybody all is well.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
